data.description: Gorgeous and relaxing WATER VIEW. THIS HOME WAS JUST BUILT IN 2020 AND IT'S STILL JUST LIKE NEW! Take advantage of the recent price improvement and the perfect time of year to make the move-up to this spacious home. ASSUMABLE VA LOAN WITH 2.5% INTEREST! Willow Bend is the affordable alternative in the area as there are NO CDD fees and Extremely LOW HOA fees! Home Warranty could be transferred to the buyer with the right offer! Beautiful curb appeal and landscaping. This impressive 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is nestled in a gorgeous neighborhood. The front bedroom can easily convert into a den/office. The open floor plan living area that welcomes you with high ceilings, ample area for entertaining, a large oversized kitchen island, a convenient walk-in pantry and abundant counter space. The master bedroom is situated off the living area with an ensuite bathroom, walk-in shower, water closet and walk-in closet. When exiting the living room sliding doors, you will be immediately drawn to the beauty and peace of the water. Enjoy the NEWLY enclosed back porch. Picture yourself sipping your morning coffee here, overlooking the peaceful waters in your own backyard. The pool Table is included! Inside, the home boasts an inviting open-concept floor plan, adorned with elegant tile throughout the main living area. Laundry room, hurricane shutters, smart garage door opener, and a Nest thermostat, two-car garage and equipped with new solar panels that significantly reduce your electric bills. Parrish keeps growing and updating. You are conveniently close to I-75, pristine beaches, top-rated schools, major airports, shopping, dining, cultural attractions, just 30 - 40 mins to professional sports teams and top beaches like,, St Pete Beach, Anna Maria Island and Siesta Key! For water enthusiasts, Gulf of Mexico Tampa Bay is just 20 minutes away and.  Tampa International, Sarasota Regional and St Pete Clearwater Airport are all within 45 minutes. Your Search Ends Here! This is a MUST SEE!
